    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS variable valve timing. This example is equipped with a 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. Significant preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rear subframe reinforcement and VANOS solenoid service to ensure structural and mechanical longevity. The suspension retains its factory-tuned geometry with updated bushings for precise turn-in. While the exterior shows minor road wear consistent with its age, the drivetrain remains robust, offering the visceral, linear power delivery and mechanical feedback characteristic of this chassis.",
      "price": 34500.0,
