    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a stellar example of a well-maintained daily driver that balances performance with everyday utility. The exterior finish retains a high gloss, showing only the minor, superficial character marks consistent with responsible road use. Inside, you will find a remarkably clean cabin featuring premium materials that have been preserved with care; the seats are firm and free of tears, and the carpets have been protected by floor mats since day one. Mechanically, the car is sound and ready for the road. It has followed a strict service schedule, resulting in a smooth-shifting transmission and a responsive engine that starts reliably in all weather conditions. All electronic components, including the infotainment system, backup camera, and climate control, function perfectly. Whether you are looking for a dependable commuter or a comfortable family vehicle, this car offers a high level of refinement and peace of mind.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
