    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that still looks great and drives even better? This car has been my trusty companion and it's in really solid shape! It\u2019s been well-loved and taken care of, so it runs super smoothly and is ready to hit the road for its next big adventure. It's the perfect balance of comfort and dependability. I\u2019d love for it to go to a good home, so come take it for a spin and see why I've enjoyed it so much!",
      "price": 32500.0,
