    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a 2004 BMW M3 (E46) finished in Carbon Black, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This example is equipped with a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory GKN variable M-differential lock. The double-VANOS system has been recently serviced, and the valve lash adjustments are within spec. To ensure structural integrity, the rear subframe mounting points have been professionally reinforced. The suspension retains its original geometry with fresh bushings and Bilstein dampers, providing the communicative feedback typical of the E46 chassis. While the exterior shows minor road-rash and light patina consistent with its mileage, the mechanical vitals are robust, offering a visceral driving experience with a linear power band and exceptional turn-in response.",
